{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Okay, I'm going to show you"},{"time":3000,"text":"again something about our diets."},{"time":6000,"text":"And I would like to know what the audience is,"},{"time":9000,"text":"and so who of you ever ate insects?"},{"time":14000,"text":"That's quite a lot."},{"time":16000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":18000,"text":"But still, you're not representing"},{"time":20000,"text":"the overall population of the Earth."},{"time":22000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":24000,"text":"Because there's 80 percent out there that really eats insects."},{"time":27000,"text":"But this is quite good."}]},{"cues":[{"time":30000,"text":"Why not eat insects? Well first, what are insects?"},{"time":33000,"text":"Insects are animals that walk around on six legs."},{"time":36000,"text":"And here you see just a selection."},{"time":38000,"text":"There's six million species of insects on this planet,"},{"time":41000,"text":"six million species."},{"time":43000,"text":"There's a few hundreds of mammals --"},{"time":45000,"text":"six million species of insects."},{"time":48000,"text":"In fact, if we count all the individual organisms,"},{"time":51000,"text":"we would come at much larger numbers."},{"time":54000,"text":"In fact, of all animals on Earth,"},{"time":57000,"text":"of all animal species,"},{"time":59000,"text":"80 percent walks on six legs."},{"time":61000,"text":"But if we would count all the individuals,"},{"time":64000,"text":"and we take an average weight of them,"},{"time":66000,"text":"it would amount to something like 200 to 2,000 kilograms"},{"time":69000,"text":"for each of you and me on Earth."},{"time":72000,"text":"That means that in terms of biomass,"},{"time":74000,"text":"insects are more abundant than we are,"},{"time":77000,"text":"and we're not on a planet of men,"},{"time":79000,"text":"but we're on a planet of insects."},{"time":82000,"text":"Insects are not only there in nature,"},{"time":84000,"text":"but they also are involved in our economy,"},{"time":86000,"text":"usually without us knowing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":88000,"text":"There was an estimation,"},{"time":90000,"text":"a conservative estimation, a couple of years ago"},{"time":92000,"text":"that the U.S. economy"},{"time":94000,"text":"benefited by 57 billion"},{"time":97000,"text":"dollars per year."},{"time":99000,"text":"It's a number -- very large --"},{"time":102000,"text":"a contribution to the economy of the United States for free."},{"time":105000,"text":"And so I looked up what the economy was paying"},{"time":108000,"text":"for the war in Iraq"},{"time":110000,"text":"in the same year."},{"time":112000,"text":"It was 80 billion U.S. dollars."},{"time":114000,"text":"Well we know that that"},{"time":116000,"text":"was not a cheap war."},{"time":118000,"text":"So insects, just for free,"},{"time":120000,"text":"contribute to the economy of the United States"},{"time":122000,"text":"with about the same order of magnitude,"},{"time":125000,"text":"just for free, without everyone knowing."},{"time":127000,"text":"And not only in the States,"},{"time":129000,"text":"but in any country, in any economy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":131000,"text":"What do they do?"},{"time":133000,"text":"They remove dung, they pollinate our crops."},{"time":135000,"text":"A third of all the fruits that we eat"},{"time":137000,"text":"are all a result"},{"time":139000,"text":"of insects taking care of the reproduction of plants."},{"time":142000,"text":"They control pests,"},{"time":144000,"text":"and they're food for animals."},{"time":146000,"text":"They're at the start of food chains."},{"time":148000,"text":"Small animals eat insects."},{"time":150000,"text":"Even larger animals eat insects."},{"time":152000,"text":"But the small animals that eat insects"},{"time":154000,"text":"are being eaten by larger animals,"},{"time":156000,"text":"still larger animals."},{"time":158000,"text":"And at the end of the food chain, we are eating them as well."},{"time":162000,"text":"There's quite a lot of people that are eating insects."},{"time":164000,"text":"And here you see me"},{"time":166000,"text":"in a small, provincial town in China, Lijiang --"},{"time":168000,"text":"about two million inhabitants."},{"time":170000,"text":"If you go out for dinner, like in a fish restaurant,"},{"time":173000,"text":"where you can select which fish you want to eat,"},{"time":176000,"text":"you can select which insects you would like to eat."},{"time":178000,"text":"And they prepare it in a wonderful way."},{"time":180000,"text":"And here you see me enjoying a meal"},{"time":182000,"text":"with caterpillars, locusts,"},{"time":185000,"text":"bee pupae -- delicacies."},{"time":188000,"text":"And you can eat something new everyday."},{"time":191000,"text":"There's more than 1,000 species of insects"},{"time":194000,"text":"that are being eaten all around the globe."},{"time":197000,"text":"That's quite a bit more"},{"time":199000,"text":"than just a few mammals that we're eating,"},{"time":201000,"text":"like a cow or a pig"},{"time":203000,"text":"or a sheep."},{"time":205000,"text":"More than 1,000 species --"},{"time":207000,"text":"an enormous variety."},{"time":210000,"text":"And now you may think, okay,"},{"time":212000,"text":"in this provincial town in China they're doing that, but not us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":215000,"text":"Well we've seen already that quite some of you"},{"time":217000,"text":"already ate insects maybe occasionally,"},{"time":220000,"text":"but I can tell you that every one of you"},{"time":222000,"text":"is eating insects, without any exception."},{"time":225000,"text":"You're eating at least"},{"time":227000,"text":"500 grams per year."},{"time":229000,"text":"What are you eating?"},{"time":231000,"text":"Tomato soup, peanut butter,"},{"time":233000,"text":"chocolate, noodles --"},{"time":235000,"text":"any processed food that you're eating"},{"time":237000,"text":"contains insects,"},{"time":239000,"text":"because insects are here all around us,"},{"time":242000,"text":"and when they're out there in nature"},{"time":244000,"text":"they're also in our crops."},{"time":246000,"text":"Some fruits get some insect damage."},{"time":249000,"text":"Those are the fruits, if they're tomato,"},{"time":251000,"text":"that go to the tomato soup."},{"time":253000,"text":"If they don't have any damage, they go to the grocery."},{"time":256000,"text":"And that's your view of a tomato."},{"time":259000,"text":"But there's tomatoes that end up in a soup,"},{"time":262000,"text":"and as long as they meet"},{"time":264000,"text":"the requirements of the food agency,"},{"time":267000,"text":"there can be all kinds of things in there,"},{"time":269000,"text":"no problem."},{"time":271000,"text":"In fact, why would we put these balls in the soup,"},{"time":274000,"text":"there's meat in there anyway?"},{"time":276000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":280000,"text":"In fact, all our processed foods"},{"time":282000,"text":"contain more proteins"},{"time":284000,"text":"than we would be aware of."},{"time":288000,"text":"So anything is a good protein source already."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291000,"text":"Now you may say,"},{"time":293000,"text":"\"Okay, so we're eating 500 grams just by accident.\""},{"time":296000,"text":"We're even doing this on purpose."},{"time":298000,"text":"In a lot of food items that we have --"},{"time":300000,"text":"I have only two items"},{"time":302000,"text":"here on the slide --"},{"time":304000,"text":"pink cookies or surimi sticks"},{"time":306000,"text":"or, if you like, Campari --"},{"time":308000,"text":"a lot of our food products that are of a red color"},{"time":311000,"text":"are dyed with a natural dye."},{"time":314000,"text":"The surimi sticks"},{"time":316000,"text":"[of] crabmeat, or is being sold as crab meat,"},{"time":318000,"text":"is white fish"},{"time":320000,"text":"that's being dyed with cochineal."},{"time":322000,"text":"Cochineal is a product"},{"time":324000,"text":"of an insect that lives off these cacti."},{"time":327000,"text":"It's being produced in large amounts,"},{"time":330000,"text":"150 to 180 metric tons per year"},{"time":333000,"text":"in the Canary Islands in Peru,"},{"time":336000,"text":"and it's big business."},{"time":338000,"text":"One gram of cochineal"},{"time":341000,"text":"costs about 30 euros."},{"time":343000,"text":"One gram of gold"},{"time":346000,"text":"is 30 euros."},{"time":349000,"text":"So it's a very precious thing"},{"time":352000,"text":"that we're using to dye our foods."}]},{"cues":[{"time":355000,"text":"Now the situation in the world is going to change"},{"time":358000,"text":"for you and me, for everyone on this Earth."},{"time":360000,"text":"The human population is growing very rapidly"},{"time":363000,"text":"and is growing exponentially."},{"time":365000,"text":"Where, at the moment, we have"},{"time":367000,"text":"something between six and seven billion people,"},{"time":369000,"text":"it will grow to about nine billion"},{"time":371000,"text":"in 2050."},{"time":374000,"text":"That means that we have a lot more mouths to feed,"},{"time":377000,"text":"and this is something that worries more and more people."},{"time":380000,"text":"There was an FAO conference last October"},{"time":382000,"text":"that was completely devoted to this."},{"time":384000,"text":"How are we going to feed this world?"},{"time":386000,"text":"And if you look at the figures up there,"},{"time":388000,"text":"it says that we have a third more mouths to feed,"},{"time":391000,"text":"but we need an agricultural production increase"},{"time":393000,"text":"of 70 percent."},{"time":395000,"text":"And that's especially because this world population"},{"time":397000,"text":"is increasing,"},{"time":399000,"text":"and it's increasing, not only in numbers,"},{"time":402000,"text":"but we're also getting wealthier,"},{"time":405000,"text":"and anyone that gets wealthier starts to eat more"},{"time":408000,"text":"and also starts to eat more meat."},{"time":411000,"text":"And meat, in fact, is something"},{"time":413000,"text":"that costs a lot"},{"time":415000,"text":"of our agricultural production."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417000,"text":"Our diet consists, [in] some part, of animal proteins,"},{"time":420000,"text":"and at the moment, most of us here"},{"time":422000,"text":"get it from livestock,"},{"time":424000,"text":"from fish, from game."},{"time":426000,"text":"And we eat quite a lot of it."},{"time":428000,"text":"In the developed world it's on average"},{"time":431000,"text":"80 kilograms per person per year,"},{"time":434000,"text":"which goes up to 120"},{"time":436000,"text":"in the United States"},{"time":438000,"text":"and a bit lower in some other countries,"},{"time":440000,"text":"but on average 80 kilograms"},{"time":442000,"text":"per person per year."},{"time":444000,"text":"In the developing world it's much lower."},{"time":447000,"text":"It's 25 kilograms per person per year."},{"time":449000,"text":"But it's increasing enormously."},{"time":451000,"text":"In China in the last 20 years,"},{"time":453000,"text":"it increased from 20 to 50,"},{"time":456000,"text":"and it's still increasing."},{"time":459000,"text":"So if a third of the world population"},{"time":462000,"text":"is going to increase its meat consumption"},{"time":465000,"text":"from 25 to 80 on average,"},{"time":468000,"text":"and a third of the world population"},{"time":470000,"text":"is living in China and in India,"},{"time":472000,"text":"we're having an enormous demand on meat."},{"time":476000,"text":"And of course, we are not there to say"},{"time":478000,"text":"that's only for us, it's not for them."},{"time":481000,"text":"They have the same share that we have."}]},{"cues":[{"time":483000,"text":"Now to start with, I should say"},{"time":485000,"text":"that we are eating way too much meat"},{"time":487000,"text":"in the Western world."},{"time":489000,"text":"We could do with much, much less --"},{"time":491000,"text":"and I know, I've been a vegetarian for a long time,"},{"time":494000,"text":"and you can easily do without anything."},{"time":496000,"text":"You'll get proteins in any kind of food anyway."},{"time":499000,"text":"But then there's a lot of problems"},{"time":501000,"text":"that come with meat production,"},{"time":503000,"text":"and we're being faced with that more and more often."},{"time":506000,"text":"The first problem that we're facing is human health."},{"time":509000,"text":"Pigs are quite like us."},{"time":511000,"text":"They're even models in medicine,"},{"time":514000,"text":"and we can even transplant organs from a pig to a human."},{"time":517000,"text":"That means that pigs also share diseases with us."},{"time":520000,"text":"And a pig disease,"},{"time":522000,"text":"a pig virus, and a human virus"},{"time":524000,"text":"can both proliferate,"},{"time":526000,"text":"and because of their kind of reproduction,"},{"time":528000,"text":"they can combine and produce a new virus."},{"time":530000,"text":"This has happened in the Netherlands in the 1990s"},{"time":533000,"text":"during the classical swine fever outbreak."},{"time":536000,"text":"You get a new disease that can be deadly."},{"time":540000,"text":"We eat insects -- they're so distantly related from us"},{"time":543000,"text":"that this doesn't happen."},{"time":545000,"text":"So that's one point for insects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":548000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":550000,"text":"And there's the conversion factor."},{"time":553000,"text":"You take 10 kilograms of feed,"},{"time":555000,"text":"you can get one kilogram of beef,"},{"time":558000,"text":"but you can get nine kilograms of locust meat."},{"time":560000,"text":"So if you would be an entrepreneur,"},{"time":562000,"text":"what would you do?"},{"time":564000,"text":"With 10 kilograms of input,"},{"time":566000,"text":"you can get either one or nine kg. of output."},{"time":569000,"text":"So far we're taking"},{"time":571000,"text":"the one, or up to five kilograms of output."},{"time":574000,"text":"We're not taking the bonus yet."},{"time":576000,"text":"We're not taking the nine kilograms of output yet."},{"time":579000,"text":"So that's two points for insects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":583000,"text":"And there's the environment."},{"time":585000,"text":"If we take 10 kilograms of food --"},{"time":587000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":589000,"text":"and it results in one kilogram of beef,"},{"time":592000,"text":"the other nine kilograms are waste,"},{"time":594000,"text":"and a lot of that is manure."},{"time":597000,"text":"If you produce insects, you have less manure"},{"time":599000,"text":"per kilogram of meat that you produce."},{"time":602000,"text":"So less waste."},{"time":604000,"text":"Furthermore, per kilogram of manure,"},{"time":607000,"text":"you have much, much less ammonia"},{"time":610000,"text":"and fewer greenhouse gases"},{"time":612000,"text":"when you have insect manure"},{"time":614000,"text":"than when you have cow manure."},{"time":616000,"text":"So you have less waste,"},{"time":618000,"text":"and the waste that you have is not as environmental malign"},{"time":621000,"text":"as it is with cow dung."},{"time":623000,"text":"So that's three points for insects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":625000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":628000,"text":"Now there's a big \"if,\" of course,"},{"time":630000,"text":"and it is if insects produce meat"},{"time":633000,"text":"that is of good quality."},{"time":635000,"text":"Well there have been all kinds of analyses"},{"time":637000,"text":"and in terms of protein, or fat, or vitamins,"},{"time":640000,"text":"it's very good."},{"time":642000,"text":"In fact, it's comparable"},{"time":644000,"text":"to anything we eat as meat at the moment."},{"time":646000,"text":"And even in terms of calories, it is very good."},{"time":648000,"text":"One kilogram of grasshoppers"},{"time":650000,"text":"has the same amount of calories"},{"time":652000,"text":"as 10 hot dogs, or six Big Macs."},{"time":654000,"text":"So that's four points for insects."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":659000,"text":"I can go on,"},{"time":661000,"text":"and I could make many more points for insects,"},{"time":663000,"text":"but time doesn't allow this."},{"time":665000,"text":"So the question is, why not eat insects?"},{"time":667000,"text":"I gave you at least four arguments in favor."},{"time":669000,"text":"We'll have to."},{"time":671000,"text":"Even if you don't like it,"},{"time":673000,"text":"you'll have to get used to this"},{"time":675000,"text":"because at the moment,"},{"time":677000,"text":"70 percent of all our agricultural land"},{"time":679000,"text":"is being used to produce livestock."},{"time":681000,"text":"That's not only the land"},{"time":683000,"text":"where the livestock is walking and feeding,"},{"time":685000,"text":"but it's also other areas"},{"time":687000,"text":"where the feed is being produced and being transported."},{"time":690000,"text":"We can increase it a bit"},{"time":692000,"text":"at the expense of rainforests,"},{"time":694000,"text":"but there's a limitation very soon."},{"time":696000,"text":"And if you remember that we need to increase"},{"time":698000,"text":"agricultural production by 70 percent,"},{"time":700000,"text":"we're not going to make it that way."},{"time":702000,"text":"We could much better change"},{"time":704000,"text":"from meat, from beef,"},{"time":707000,"text":"to insects."},{"time":709000,"text":"And then 80 percent of the world"},{"time":712000,"text":"already eats insects,"},{"time":714000,"text":"so we are just a minority --"},{"time":716000,"text":"in a country like the U.K., the USA,"},{"time":719000,"text":"the Netherlands, anywhere."},{"time":722000,"text":"On the left-hand side, you see a market in Laos"},{"time":724000,"text":"where they have abundantly present"},{"time":726000,"text":"all kinds of insects that you choose for dinner for the night."},{"time":731000,"text":"On the right-hand side you see a grasshopper."},{"time":733000,"text":"So people there are eating them,"},{"time":736000,"text":"not because they're hungry,"},{"time":738000,"text":"but because they think it's a delicacy."},{"time":740000,"text":"It's just very good food."},{"time":742000,"text":"You can vary enormously."},{"time":744000,"text":"It has many benefits."}]},{"cues":[{"time":746000,"text":"In fact, we have delicacy"},{"time":748000,"text":"that's very much like this grasshopper:"},{"time":750000,"text":"shrimps, a delicacy"},{"time":753000,"text":"being sold at a high price."},{"time":755000,"text":"Who wouldn't like to eat a shrimp?"},{"time":757000,"text":"There are a few people who don't like shrimp,"},{"time":759000,"text":"but shrimp, or crabs,"},{"time":761000,"text":"or crayfish,"},{"time":763000,"text":"are very closely related."},{"time":765000,"text":"They are delicacies."},{"time":767000,"text":"In fact, a locust is a \"shrimp\" of the land,"},{"time":770000,"text":"and it would make very good into our diet."},{"time":773000,"text":"So why are we not eating insects yet?"},{"time":775000,"text":"Well that's just a matter of mindset."},{"time":777000,"text":"We're not used to it,"},{"time":779000,"text":"and we see insects as these organisms that are very different from us."},{"time":782000,"text":"That's why we're changing the perception of insects."},{"time":785000,"text":"And I'm working very hard with my colleague, Arnold van Huis,"},{"time":788000,"text":"in telling people what insects are,"},{"time":791000,"text":"what magnificent things they are,"},{"time":793000,"text":"what magnificent jobs they do in nature."},{"time":795000,"text":"And in fact, without insects,"},{"time":797000,"text":"we would not be here in this room,"},{"time":799000,"text":"because if the insects die out,"},{"time":801000,"text":"we will soon die out as well."},{"time":804000,"text":"If we die out, the insects will continue very happily."}]},{"cues":[{"time":807000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":809000,"text":"So we have to get used to the idea of eating insects."},{"time":811000,"text":"And some might think, well they're not yet available."},{"time":813000,"text":"Well they are."},{"time":815000,"text":"There are entrepreneurs in the Netherlands that produce them,"},{"time":818000,"text":"and one of them is here in the audience,"},{"time":820000,"text":"Marian Peeters, who's in the picture."},{"time":822000,"text":"I predict that later this year, you'll get them in the supermarkets --"},{"time":825000,"text":"not visible, but as animal protein"},{"time":827000,"text":"in the food."},{"time":831000,"text":"And maybe by 2020,"},{"time":834000,"text":"you'll buy them just knowing that this is an insect that you're going to eat."},{"time":837000,"text":"And they're being made in the most wonderful ways."},{"time":840000,"text":"A Dutch chocolate maker."},{"time":843000,"text":"(Music)"},{"time":880000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":882000,"text":"So there's even a lot of design to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":884000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":887000,"text":"Well in the Netherlands, we have an innovative Minister of Agriculture,"},{"time":890000,"text":"and she puts the insects on the menu"},{"time":892000,"text":"in her restaurant in her ministry."},{"time":895000,"text":"And when she got all the Ministers of Agriculture of the E.U."},{"time":898000,"text":"over to the Hague recently,"},{"time":901000,"text":"she went to a high-class restaurant,"},{"time":904000,"text":"and they ate insects all together."},{"time":906000,"text":"It's not something that is a hobby of mine."},{"time":909000,"text":"It's really taken off the ground."},{"time":911000,"text":"So why not eat insects?"},{"time":913000,"text":"You should try it yourself."},{"time":915000,"text":"A couple of years ago, we had 1,750 people all together"},{"time":918000,"text":"in a square in Wageningen town,"},{"time":921000,"text":"and they ate insects at the same moment,"},{"time":923000,"text":"and this was still big, big news."},{"time":926000,"text":"I think soon it will not be big news anymore when we all eat insects,"},{"time":929000,"text":"because it's just a normal way of doing."}]},{"cues":[{"time":931000,"text":"So you can try it yourself today,"},{"time":934000,"text":"and I would say, enjoy."},{"time":937000,"text":"And I'm going to show to Bruno some first tries,"},{"time":940000,"text":"and he can have the first bite."}]},{"cues":[{"time":943000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":955000,"text":"Bruno Giussani: Look at them first. Look at them first."}]},{"cues":[{"time":958000,"text":"Marcel Dicke: It's all protein."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961000,"text":"BG: That's exactly the same [one] you saw in the video actually."},{"time":964000,"text":"And it looks delicious."},{"time":966000,"text":"They just make it [with] nuts or something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":969000,"text":"MD: Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":971000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}